summary: Hey there! Have you heard about the Avengers initiative? Well… There was an idea, called the Avengers Initiative. The idea was...
caption:
Hey there! Have you heard about the Avengers initiative? Well… There was an idea, called the Avengers Initiative. The idea was to bring together a group of remarkable people, see if they could become something more.

And it failed

EPICALLY

Thanos kicked their ass, snapped his fingers and wiped out half the living things in the universe… So this is where I come in… No… this is where WE come in.

I, your friendly neighborhood Deadpool have made this RP where I have traveled back in time to recruit SUPER AWESOME ROLEPLAYERS to play the Avengers, X-men and other members of the Marvel Universe to form the new, superior Super Hero team.

AX FORCE

summary:
Miles: Peter! Why did you travel through the multiverse again? Is it an emergency!? Are we going to die!?
Peter: No. Much more...
body:
Miles: Peter! Why did you travel through the multiverse again? Is it an emergency!? Are we going to die!?

Peter: No. Much more important…*Pulls a picture of a red haired baby girl out of his jacket* MJ and I just had a baby! Isn’t she adorable? She’s named May but we gave her the Mayday as a nickname and she is the cutest and most precious thing in the entire world!

Miles: You risked making the multiverse collapse…because you wanted to show me baby pictures!?

Peter: I also showed Gwen, Peni, Noir, Miguel and Ham.
